               cmake,
               libssl-dev,
               pkg-config,
               python3-sphinx,
               zlib1g-dev,
               libicu-dev,
               libsasl2-dev,
               libsnappy-dev
Standards-Version: 4.1.4
Section: libs
Homepage: https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-c-driver
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-c-driver.git
